<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-8722] Update BUILDING.txt with latest snappy info</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-8722</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-8620&quot; title=&quot;Add -Drequire.fuse and -Drequire.snappy&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-8620&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-8620&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; changed the default of snappy.lib from snappy.prefix/lib to empty.  This, in turn, means that you can&apos;t use &lt;tt&gt;-Dbundle.snappy&lt;/tt&gt; without setting &lt;tt&gt;-Dsnappy.lib&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
